The skill isn't doing what I thought it would do, or what other people have said it would do. This means its doing something that we don't know is going on with taunt. This could be in a few particular cases, this could occur on a smaller scale everywhere and in every case, we really don't know. I would love to know what is going on here, if for nothing more than it would allow me to be a better player.<br />
