I've seen the 4-taunt-to-succeed "bug" happen when *I* had pulled the mob with prox aggro (/con pulling werks gud!).  Seemed quite repeatable with sol ro tower trash, I pull mob, have chanter mez, then boggle before breaking mez.  Mob takes absolutely no damage till I break mez with slam/taunt/autoattack, but requires 4+ taunts to get it off the chanter.  <br />
